high_descs: Turn and go to the small table by the sofa.
Pick up the remote control on the small table.
Turn and go to the armchair in the corner.
Put the remote control on the armchair.
Turn and go to the sofa.
Pick up the remote control on the sofa.
Turn and go to the armchair in the corner.
Put the remote control on the armchair.
anns.task_desc: Move two remote controls to the armchair in the corner.

high_descs: Turn around, walk to the painting on the wall and turn left to face the black cabinet.
Pick up the remote control from on top of the cabinet.
Go to the left a little bit, turn right and walk to the chair next to the fireplace.
Put the remote control horizontally on the chair.
Turn around, walk straight and turn right to face the couch that has a green pillow on it.
Pick up another remote control from on top of the couch.
Go back to the chair next to the fireplace again.
Put the remote control vertically so they make the letter J on the chair.
anns.task_desc: Put 2 remote controls so they make a letter J on the chair next to the fireplace.

high_descs: Go to the small black cabinet
Pick up the remote on top of the cabinet
Go to the couch
Place the remote on the couch
Go to the sofa
Pick up the remote from the sofa
Go to the couch
Place the remote on the couch next to the other remote
anns.task_desc: Move two remotes to a couch
